ingdata.com/tag/ownership/" rel="tag">所有权</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/perplexity/" rel="tag">困惑</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/wired/" rel="tag">连线</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> Dhruv Mehrotra 和 Tim Marchman 为《连线》提供了证据，证明 Perplexity 这家基于人工智能的公司目前估值达 10 亿美元，<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/perplexity-is-a-bullshit-machine/">似乎正在吞噬他们能得到的一切</a>：</p><blockquote><p>在某些情况下，尽管用户界面中的图形表示显示聊天机器人在回复提示之前“阅读”特定的源材料，但困惑也可能不是在总结实际的新闻文章，而是根据他们所说的内容进行重建。搜索引擎中留下的 URL 及其痕迹（例如摘录和元数据），提供据称基于直接访问相关文本的摘要。</p><p>换句话说，让 Perplexity 值 10 位数的魔术似乎是它既在做它所说的不做的事情，又不做它所说的事情。</p></blockquote><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ethics/" rel="tag">道德</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ownership/" rel="tag">所有权</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/perplexity/" rel="tag">困惑</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/wired/" rel="tag">连线</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 74479</post-id></item><item><title> AI 生成的来自朋友的电子邮件</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/06/20/ai- generated-email-from-a-friend/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 20 Jun 2024 07:24:18 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistics]]></category><category><![CDATA[AI]]></category><category><![CDATA[email]]></category><category><![CDATA[Neven Mrgan]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=74453 </guid><description><![CDATA[Neven Mrgan describes what it was like to get an AI-generated email from&#8230;<p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/email/" rel="tag">电子邮件</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/neven-mrgan/" rel="tag">内文·摩根</a></p>]]>; </description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p> Neven Mrgan 描述了<a href="https://mrgan.com/ai-email-from-a-friend/">从朋友那里收到人工智能生成的电子邮件</a>的感觉：</p><blockquote><p>我知道我不需要算法来设计布局和绘制插图，“所以我不必这样做”，但在这封电子邮件之前，我什至从未考虑过我是否希望人工智能代表我身边的人给我打电话。生活。我根本没有想到这一点，现在我已经想到了，我绝对不希望闲聊和关系外包给服务器场。这些东西不应该让人感到困难或费力；这就是我们在地球上的存在的主要组成部分。付出的努力、笨拙和投入的时间，都是人性的储存之处。</p></blockquote><p>我收到了一个有关 FlowingData 链接的警报，该链接是针对一个草率的人工智能生成的网站。该网站涵盖了各种主题，包括生成的标题、文本和封面图像。它表面上看起来像一个新闻网站，但一旦你尝试阅读，它就失去了所有意义。</p><p>其中一篇“文章”是我写的一些内容的“摘要”。这感觉既懒惰又无礼，这听起来很熟悉摩根对他朋友的“电子邮件”的感觉。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/ai/" rel="tag">人工智能</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/email/" rel="tag">电子邮件</a>、<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/neven-mrgan/" rel="tag">内文·摩根</a></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 74453</post-id></item><item><title>美国热追踪器</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2024/06/19/heat-tracker-for-the-us/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 19 Jun 2024 07:40:58 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Statistical Visualization]]></category><category><![CDATA[heat]]></category><category><![CDATA[New York Times]]></category><category><![CDATA[warning]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=74456 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2024/06/19/heat-tracker-for-the-u-s/"><img width="750" height="436" src="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heat-index-forecast.png?fit=750%2C436&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heat-index-forecast.png?w=1814&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1 1814w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heat-index-forecast.png?resize=750%2C436&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1 750w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heat-index-forecast.png?resize=1090%2C634&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1 1090w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/heat-index-forecast.png?resize=210%2C122&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1 210w, https://i0.wp.com/flowin