p.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/tic-tac-toe.png?resize=768%2C756&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/tic-tac-toe.png?resize=1536%2C1512&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" data-attachment-id="74415" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2024/06/14/probabilistic-tic-tac-toe/tic-tac-toe/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/tic-tac-toe.png?fit=1802%2C1774&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1802,1774" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="tic-tac-toe" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/tic-tac-toe.png?fit=750%2C738&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/tic-tac-toe.png?fit=1090%2C1073&amp;quality=80&amp;ssl=1" /></a></p><p>出于对生活和随机性的思考， <a href="https://www.csun.io/2024/06/08/probabilistic-tic-tac-toe.html">Cameron Sun修改了经典游戏“井字游戏”</a> 。您可以选择自己想去的地方，但无法控制结果：</p><blockquote><p>在任何给定的概率井字游戏中，您可以做所有正确的事情，但仍然会失败（或者做所有错误的事情并获胜）。但是，随着时间的推移，更好的玩家总是会上升到顶峰。我发现许多其他游戏都具有这些有趣的特征，并且我认为将它们应用到像井字游戏这样无聊的、已解决的游戏中会很有趣。它们也与我的人生哲学高度相关——每个结果实际上都是随机的，但我们的行为往往可以使胜算对我们有利。糟糕的突破是不可避免的，但良好的判断总是会得到回报（最终，并给予足够的机会。）</p></blockquote><p>该代码可<a href="https://github.com/csun/probabilistic-tic-tac-toe">在 GitHub 上</a>获取。</p><p><strong>标签：</strong> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/cameron-sun/" rel="tag">Cameron Sun</a> ,<a href="https://flowingdata.com/tag/game/" rel="tag">游戏</a>,<a h